import React from 'react'
import {NavFlex, MenuLink, NavLogo, BeRide} from './style'
import {GiFlamingTrident} from 'react-icons/gi'

const NavBar = () => {
    return (
        <NavFlex>
            <NavLogo>
                <MenuLink href="/">
                    <GiFlamingTrident/>  
                </MenuLink>
                <MenuLink href="/">
                    <BeRide>BeRide</BeRide>    
                </MenuLink>
            </NavLogo>
            <NavMenu>
                <MenuLink href="/about"><MenuP>New</MenuP></MenuLink>
                <MenuLink href="/about"><MenuP>RACEWEAR</MenuP></MenuLink>
                <MenuLink href="/about"><MenuP>STREETWEAR</MenuP></MenuLink>
                <MenuLink href="/about"><MenuP>IN</MenuP></MenuLink>
                <MenuLink href="/about"><MenuP>New</MenuP></MenuLink>
            </NavMenu>

        </NavFlex>
    )
}

export default NavBar
